---
import Layout from '../layouts/Default.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import profileImage from '../assets/pieter-de-jong-300.png';
---

<Layout
	title="Software Engineer and Mathematician"
	description="Homepage of Pieter de Jong, Software Engineer and Mathematician"
>
<main>
    <div class="bio-container">
        <div class="bio-left">
            <div class="profile-image-container">
                <Image 
                    src={profileImage}
                    alt="Pieter de Jong" 
                    class="profile-image"
                    width={300}
                    height={300}
                />
                <div class="profile-info">
                    <h2>Pieter de Jong</h2>
                    <a href="/contact" class="button-link">Contact</a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pieteradejong/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="accent-link">LinkedIn</a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/pieteradejong" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="accent-link">GitHub</a>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bio-right">
        <p>
            Hi, I'm Pieter. I'm a software engineer with industry experience since 2012, in industries including consumer finance, ecommerce, digital agriculture, Big Data, medical Q&amp;A, interpersonal experiences, and solar energy. Companies ranging from seed-stage to series A/B to publicly traded.
        </p>
        <p>
            In my professional life, I've built and contributed to full stack web applications, React Native mobile apps, data pipelines, multi-million user ecommerce platforms, mission-critical user registration flows, developed Big Data educational curriculum, and developed foundational features for premium social experiences. I also use AI/LLM-based tools on a daily basis to increase my coding productivity. Finally, I've worked side by side with Founders/CEOs/CTOs to plan product strategy and brainstorm company strategy and product market fit.
        </p>
        <p>
            Over my life, I've enjoyed sports including skiing and snowboarding, hiking, judo, and kickboxing group classes. In my free time, I pay attention to geopolitics, and aspirationally I'd like to study Classical Greek and Latin as I did in high school.
        </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<style>
    .bio-container {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--spacing-xl);
        max-width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .bio-left {
        flex: 0 0 min(33.333%, 300px);
        max-width: min(33.333%, 300px);
    }

    .bio-right {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 0; /* Prevents flex item from overflowing */
    }

    .profile-image-container {
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-large);
        width: 100%;
    }

    .profile-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        aspect-ratio: 1;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border: 3px solid var(--border);
    }

    .profile-info {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: var(--spacing-unit);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .profile-info h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: var(--font-size-h2);
        color: var(--primary-text);
    }

    /* Tablet Layout */
    @media (max-width: 1023px) {
        .bio-container {
            gap: var(--spacing-large);
        }

        .bio-left {
            flex: 0 0 min(40%, 250px);
            max-width: min(40%, 250px);
        }
    }

    /* Mobile Layout */
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
        .bio-container {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--spacing-large);
        }

        .bio-left {
            display: none;
        }

        .bio-right {
            max-width: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            margin-top: var(--spacing-unit);
        }

        .profile-info {
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
    }
</style>
</Layout>
